snippet.title: Virtual Hunter | Graphics And Vegetation Update Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
The next Virtual Hunter's update will completely rework most of the graphics, lighting, vegetation, add more grass and much more! The update is a significant upgrade and will immerse you in the game like never before. Coming very soon!

Get the game from Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1549850/Virtual_Hunter

Join our Discord server: https://discord.gg/gGmSAA8Prd
